Upload an attachment to the server's iMessage attachments directory.

This is a pre-requisite and _must_ be done before sending an attachment as part of a _multipart_ message. This is **not** required when sending a normal attachment.

The response of this endpoint will be a unique identifier that you can use when sending a _multipart_ message.

#### Example Response

``` json
{
    "status": 200,
    "message": "Success",
    "data": {
        "hash": "a04a23a0833b33db8a63ee0816948786"
    }
}

```

